high_descs: Turn left and walk around to the far end of the table.
Pick up the dog statue on the table.
Turn left and move around the table to the living room, then turn right and face the lounge chair closest to the TV.
Turn the lamp on to the left of the lounge chair.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp to the left of the lounge chair to inspect the dog statue.

high_descs: Walk to the wall, turn left, walk to the end of the kitchen table, turn left, then turn left again to face the side of the kitchen table.
Pick up the animal figurine that is sitting on the table.
Turn to the left, walk to the window, turn right, walk up to the chair, make a right, walk up to the television stand, then turn right and walk up to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a figurine using the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the statue on the dining table near the laptops.
Pick up the statue from the table.
Walk around the left side of the dining table to the gray armchair, then turn right and walk across the room to the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue by the light of a floor lamp.
